graph TD
    Start(开始) --> InputLoginId[输入登录标识（邮箱或用户名）]
    InputLoginId --> InputLoginPassword[输入登录密码]
    InputLoginPassword --> SubmitLogin[提交登录信息]
    SubmitLogin --> CheckLoginInfo{检查登录信息是否正确}
    CheckLoginInfo --> |不正确| ShowLoginError[提示登录失败]
    ShowLoginError --> InputLoginId
    CheckLoginInfo --> |正确| CheckAccountStatus{检查账户状态是否正常}
    CheckAccountStatus --> |账户异常| ShowAccountProblem[提示账户存在问题,联系管理员]
    ShowAccountProblem --> End(结束)
    CheckAccountStatus --> |账户正常| CheckEmailVerified{检查邮箱是否已验证}
    CheckEmailVerified --> |未验证| PromptEmailVerification[提示进行邮箱验证]
    PromptEmailVerification --> SendNewVerificationEmail{选择重新发送验证邮件}
    SendNewVerificationEmail --> |是| SendVerificationEmail[发送新的验证邮件]
    SendNewVerificationEmail --> |否| End
    SendVerificationEmail --> End
    CheckEmailVerified --> |已验证| LoginSuccess[登录成功,进入系统]
    LoginSuccess --> RecordLoginHistory[记录登录历史]
    RecordLoginHistory --> ShowUserDashboard[显示用户个人面板]
    ShowUserDashboard --> End